name: Gates Of Elysium
description: My first encounter with Elysium’s gate, half crumbling and jagged, lost in time at the entrance of Paradise - Animated from two paintings by Ferdinand Knab, 19thC - Text taken from poems by John Milton “Paradise Lost” & William Arthur Dunkerley “The Gate” & Lord Byron “Childe Harold’s Pilgrimage” - Produced and performed by Laurence Fuller @laurencefuller
